ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"其實又真估唔到拜登照侵個DEAL撤兵喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔支持撒，不過邊個做總統都會撒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d459ca4f12ffe5429e5440251d8f7653ff2f1f","tid":2489411,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd9f18628fb94ed69d84f819dc56f112ec9a5783","tid":2489411,"uid":68620,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"維尼未過數咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"幼幼未打針唔過得關"},{"pid":"4d0ce78c8d485fddca31a79ef38d169cc0db7abf","tid":2489411,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"維吾爾幼幼未到?"},{"pid":"bd5f7df632dd63cdc5a758031d9d51385dc045a9","tid":2489411,"uid":290393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2397e904af9b9ba2b458a6037cf5ddfc92ac2311","tid":2489411,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cfd5f742587601c0e2322df9c4b995311e0f28d","tid":2489411,"uid":290393,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58da44f11c7fbe5727ba4c631412e2804f24ea6b","tid":2489411,"uid":271513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"good 中東搵盟友以色列搞啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"當年阿侵退兵, 左膠鳩叫咪話佢放棄庫爾德人嘅? 佢地就快進場, 話拜登總統放棄阿富汗人比塔利班架啦 (應該) <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"其實又真估唔到拜登照侵個DEAL撤兵喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔支持撒，不過邊個做總統都會撒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔駛估唔到, 因為奧巴馬果陣都想撒, 但佢撒唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係政客同商人分別, 商人講止蝕, 但政客講的是權勢. 例如一戰, 如果德國係商人心態, 可能寧願奧匈輸少少都唔會一次跟哂機<br />\n<br />\n阿侵如果呢件事有乜野突破, 就係佢只係面對同正視, 阿富汗個形勢, 係無得贏, 亦無野值得贏. 阿富汗唔係美國殖民地, 亦毫無好處. 除左&quot;正義&quot;, 同埋叫做希望恐怖主義唔好燒到本土, 佢根本無好處<br />\n<br />\n而阿侵個用途就係正視只能止蝕離場, 同塔利班deal. 咁概然有做, 個局勢無以前咁差, 到呢任其實一定想退<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知你政見唔同, 但你都要明白, 好多正確決定, 往往就係阿侵果個決定. D人只係搞緊文化大革命, 要奪權先人蔘攻擊佢<br />\n<br />\n講真, 阿侵未做總統前, 一直係荷里活同紐約好多朋友, 佢有乜野仆街同歧視, 一早通哂天啦. 佢只係一個藉口黎<br />\n<br />\n不過講遠左, 拜登佢係唔掂, 但佢做正確野都應該支持, 而且呢個係佢功勞"},{"pid":"ab6bc76aafe4dec68c0e74dfc4ea272ea9b21c67","tid":2489411,"uid":51148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"唔係話敗登同翠翠打龍通咩？<br />\n依家咁強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得係侵侵拎住左實權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0674e31623a0e508e3a61b415d89372213ac7fe","tid":2489411,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd9f18628fb94ed69d84f819dc56f112ec9a5783","tid":2489411,"uid":68620,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"維尼未過數咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://twgreatdaily.com/images/elastic/XsU/XsUvF3IBfGB4SiUw00bp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwgreatdaily.com%2Fimages%2Felastic%2FXsU%2FXsUvF3IBfGB4SiUw00bp.jpg&h=38271847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大頭幻幻"},{"pid":"4d1ee40b9e6c5e40876052d4a82cc52803d1d8aa","tid":2489411,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"介紹中國俾塔利班, 玩個邊好玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1acb863deea65c3a3d7ab5107c995973e4d739","tid":2489411,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01263b57a02286348f2a98156700e02185a7f9bd","tid":2489411,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1d1a060477515220795f0c31d294c8db3c22179","tid":2489411,"uid":52658,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"拜登說，在做這個決定之前，他與兩位前總統小布殊以及奧巴馬都討論過，他們兩位都支持這個決定。<br />\n<br />\n點解就係唔同川普討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><